snippet.title: THE JOY OF CREATION | OFFICIAL DEMO TRAILER
snippet.description:
THE JOY OF CREATION is a complete re-imagining of all previous TJOC games bringing a new direction to the classic and beloved series of Five Nights at Freddy's fan-games.

I'm thrilled to finally show you all a first look at the gameplay, and have you all be able to experience the office demo on August 2nd !

Wishlist the game on Steam here! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2948730/THE_JOY_OF_CREATION
